<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Adoption Application Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h2>Adoption Application Confirmation</h2>
    <p>Dear <strong>
            <%= adopterName %>
        </strong>,</p>
    <p>Thank you for applying to adopt <strong>
            <%= animalType %>
        </strong> with the code <strong>
            <%= animalCode %>
        </strong>.</p>
    <p>Your application details are as follows:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Name:</strong>
            <%= adopterName %>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong>
            <%= contactEmail %>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Phone:</strong>
            <%= contactPhone %>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Address:</strong>
            <%= address %>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Experience:</strong>
            <%= experience %>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <p>We will review your application and get back to you shortly.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>Your Adoption Team</p>
</body>

</html>